config file:            ~/.i3/config
menu:                   $mod+d
stack mode:             $mod+s <-> $mod+e
tab mode:               $mod+w <-> $mod+e

custom wallpaper:       use 'feh'
Media keys:             view file media_keys
find window's class:    use 'xprop' (second value)
Awesome font (icons):   view file 'fonts_fontawesome'
Change system font:     view file 'fonts_systemfont' (clue: use 'lxappearance')
Change Icons:           use 'lxappearance'
Change Theme:           use 'lxappearance' (arc theme: https://github.com/horst3180/Arc-theme)
i3blocks:               view file i3bar
Capture key code:       use 'xev'
